  "title": "Entra ID Purple-teaming with Dr Azure AD",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael and Sarah talk with guest Dr. Nestori Syynimaa [Dr Azure AD]&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/nestori/?originalSubdomain=fi'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/DrAzureAD'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about Entra ID security and his purple-team tool, AADInternals. \n\n                  <br>\n                  We also discuss Azure Security news about Secure Future Initiative (SFI), MFA for Azure Portal, Playright, WordPress, NSG, Bastion, Azure Functions, MS Ignite, App Service, Defender for Cloud, Containers, Azure Monitor, AKS, Trustworthy AI and Azure AI Content Safety.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/1689814?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1689814/\">DrAzureAd</a></iframe>\n\n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1689814/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/security/blog/2024/09/23/securing-our-future-september-2024-progress-update-on-microsofts-secure-future-initiative-sfi/\">Securing our future: September 2024 progress update on Microsoft’s Secure Future Initiative (SFI)\n                     </a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\